(21572, 'Lamisil 125mg 14 tab.', 'لاميزيل 125مجم 14 قرص', '', '50', 'Terbinafine', 'Novartis', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antifungals.allylamines', '125mg', 'Terbinafine hydrochloride is indicated to treat fungal skin and nail infections caused by _Trichophyton_ species, _Microsporum canis_, _Epidermophyton floccosum_,[L9068] and _Tinea_ species.[L9065] Terbinafine hydrochloride also treats yeast infections of the skin caused by _Candida_ species and _Malassezia furfur_.[L9068]', '6223002641789', '', 963, '2022-12-06', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
